{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Broadcast_Channel_API\">Broadcast Channel API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>BroadcastChannel</strong></code> 接口代理了一个命名频道，可以让指定&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Origin\">origin</a> 下的任意&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Browsing_context\">browsing context</a> 来订阅它。它允许同源的不同浏览器窗口，Tab 页，frame 或者 iframe 下的不同文档之间相互通信。通过触发一个&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> 事件，消息可以广播到所有监听了该频道的&nbsp;<code>BroadcastChannel</code> 对象。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 此特性在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 中可用</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"broadcastchannel\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\" title=\"BroadcastChannel()\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>创建一个链接到命名频道的对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>该接口会从它的父级 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> 继承属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"broadcastchannel.name\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>BroadcastChannel.name</code></a></dt>\n <dd>频道名称，返回 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 。</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n <h3 id=\"事件处理程序\">事件处理程序</h3>\n </dt>\n <dt id=\"broadcastchannel.onmessage\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\"><code>BroadcastChannel.onmessage</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> ，用于定义当该对象上触发了&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> 事件时要执行的函数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"broadcastchannel.onmessageerror\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>BroadcastChannel.onmessageerror</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> ，用于定义当该对象上触发了类型为&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MessageError</code></a> 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> 事件时要执行的函数。当接收到一条无法反序列化的消息时会触发此事件。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>该接口会从它的父级 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> 继承方法。</em></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>BroadcastChannel.postMessage()</code></a></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dd>向所有监听了相同频道的&nbsp;<code>BroadcastChannel</code> 对象发送一条消息，消息内容可以是任意类型的数据。&nbsp;</dd>\n <dt id=\"broadcastchannel.close\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>BroadcastChannel.close()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>关闭频道对象，告诉它不要再接收新的消息，并允许它最终被垃圾回收。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件","title":"事件","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"message\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\">message</a></code></dt>\n <dd>当频道收到一条消息时触发。<br>\n 也可以使用 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\">onmessage</a></code> 属性访问。</dd>\n <dt id=\"messageerror\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\">messageerror</a></code></dt>\n <dd>当频道收到一条无法反序列化的消息时触发。<br>\n 也可以使用 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\">onmessageerror</a></code> 属性访问。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-messaging.html#broadcasting-to-other-browsing-contexts","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.BroadcastChannel"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>一种在不同浏览器上下文之间通信的重量级方案：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a>。</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Broadcast_Channel_API\">Broadcast Channel API overview</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"事件","id":"事件"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"BroadcastChannel 接口代理了一个命名频道，可以让指定 origin 下的任意 browsing context 来订阅它。它允许同源的不同浏览器窗口，Tab 页，frame 或者 iframe 下的不同文档之间相互通信。通过触发一个 message 事件，消息可以广播到所有监听了该频道的 BroadcastChannel 对象。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BroadcastChannel","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/broadcastchannel","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/broadcastchannel/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel","title":"BroadcastChannel"}],"pageTitle":"BroadcastChannel - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}